column2: SELECT j.objid, info.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid , i.d4#_n, e.lgm_tot_p5#, e.sfr_tot_p5#, l.h_beta_flux, l.oiii_#_flux, l.h_alpha_flux, l.nii_#_flux into mydb.jtab_index from specObjAll s JOIN MyDB.jtab j ON j.objid = s.bestObjID JOIN galSpecInfo info ON info.plateid = s.plate and info.mjd = s.mjd and info.fiberid = s.fiberID JOIN galSpecLine l ON l.specObjID = info.specObjID JOIN galSpecExtra e ON e.specObjID = info.specObjID JOIN galSpecIndx i ON i.specObjID = info.specObjID
